Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will they keep a loser like me in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:05.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:05.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:10.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:11.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is, of course there is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:19.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Shoji Tomoharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No shouting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:23.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mikitty! No spray version \N  -An original
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:26.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because of the epidemic  \N-Epidemic Limited Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:29.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So folks, it's not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The lecture series, we all like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:34.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is such a series
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm bringing a new perspective on the lecture series today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:38.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:38.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are there any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it, please take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:45.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,While lecturing someone, it's ok to add Nagabuchi's lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:47.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi Nagabuchi, I really like his stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kakuta, do you like him too? \N -I like him
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A lot of his lyrics are like tenets of life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also like him a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:06.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So wouldn't it be a good idea to mix his lyrics in while lecturing someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:09.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His words themselves are all very good \N -No doubt about it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The problem is how to blend them in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:14.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't do it when flirting with someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no. \N -Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He has a song called "Captain of the Ship" which is 13 minutes long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:22.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can just use all of the last seven minutes, right?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:24.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?\N  -It's true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's all about uplifting sentences \N -Yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:29.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's all about "live and let live" and "you must finish"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you that obsessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're really the worst, seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, what he's saying is weird
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's because his lyrics are really inspiring. \N -That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:48.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the person realizes, the lecture will end immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:50.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:55.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you have a strong will, you can control your body even after falling asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:57.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:04.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are no residents whose nearest station is "Meibijo Station" on the Tokyo Monorail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:27.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正韵动特黑简体\fs55\c&H17FFFA&\bord0\b0\shad3\4c&H000000&} \N{\r}While lecturing someone, it's ok to add Nagabuchi's lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the first challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:32.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Moriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:45.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As per the theory, the contestants will choose from the following 10 famous songs written by Tsuyoshi Nagabuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Moriyama's choice is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In terms of what is better to include in a lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nagabuchi's "Dragonfly"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:03:01.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The famous song "Dragonfly", which became a household name as the theme song of the drama of the same name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:06.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Came from Osaka to Tokyo resonates with me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:09.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This song is also very much in line with my own situation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the most suitable for my current situation is "Dragonfly"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:36.80,special_Wed_1_1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\xshad4\yshad5\pos(400.5,832)\org(402,804)\frx-270\t(0,150,\frx-360)}※If the lyrics are spoken incorrectly{\c&H1B01D7&}the score will be reduced
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:20.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, the lyrics are divided into ten levels according to the difficulty of adding the lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must be tought
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The shorter the lyric, the less the score
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,To the north to the north is only 3 points
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With a time limit of 30 minutes, the highest score wins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:27.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But if in the process of lecturing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:32.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They will be disqualified if the other person points out the lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Normally you wouldn't point out something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The juniors who are the targets are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kyon's Cotten, a Tokyo-based junior
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:51.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A junior of Moriyama's for five years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's probably not a bad choice.  \N-Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This kid seems quite innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably a good target
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You think he won't realize? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:07.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A fake project of "2-shot talk with comedians who are close"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kyon is called to participate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:14.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,While waiting for the official filming, the "Dragonfly" lecture begins
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:15.71,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dragonfly lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:20.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many lyrics can be mixed in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How is Nishimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:25.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I saw your show...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you.  \N-It was fun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I liked that part
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:33.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:36.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That high school girl
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah Sachiko? Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:43.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that a character you use in the theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:48.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, that's just for the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should continue with the character
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:54.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since it's popular its best to run with it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should definitely keep using it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:57.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:58.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But to have a persona isn't enough
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:04.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}As if standing there with an irrelevant face
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:05.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So impressive, so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,And he agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:16.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to grow up to be a person like you in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean mean be a person like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From the masters to the seniors who are near the same level as you, everyone supports you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm not that good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:27.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}I'm just praying to stay true to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh so cool
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He said cool
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't notice? He even said cool
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Risky move
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although the lecture itself is a little weak
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:47.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So far, Moriyama has not been discovered, and the lyrics of "Dragonfly" have been added naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Samurai SLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They've come to Osaka, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:51.01,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※In April 2021, Samurai SLICE moved from Yoshimoto, Tokyo to Yoshimoto, Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Came to Osaka and were immediately invited to the theater there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:58.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's great that they dared to move to Osaka.\N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:02.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What they are doing now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:05.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Will they keep a loser like me in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a bit too much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,As long as they don't notice it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean keep in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I usually look up words I don't know when I come across them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:21.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:27.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Samurai SLICE's performance in Osaka was also very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:30.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very good, really interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:33.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, especially in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}It makes people feel like sitting on pins and needles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sitting on pins and needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to sit on pins and needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Moriyama is really a man of culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:47.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are too uneducated, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:53.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nagabuchi's unique use of words and phrases, which are not used in everyday conversation, arouses suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, so unique
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unexpected, Moriyama experiences a crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So many words i've never heard today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:04.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it seems the lyrics don't immediately come up when searched, so he's safe for now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Checking immediately when encountering
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But you create things like this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Where are you going to fly next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:19.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To win the King of Conte
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:25.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You yourself are also {\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4} counting the nights you can't bear {\r} to cheer yourself up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I actually counted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only 5 minutes remain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was a good choice. \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:40.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kyon is very underdeveloped in regard to detecting "Dragonflys"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, Moriyama pushes ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:49.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, after listening to you face to face, I really think you look very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}I think you look like a happy dragonfly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too much too much
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A happy dragonfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:01.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you were compared to a dragonfly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is the happy dragonfly Nagabuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)}Really, do a good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Moriyama Disqualified
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So at this point, the truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Betting on a big one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you lecturing? Moriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was scared when this kid kept checking things
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was so scared that I couldn't breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challengers are
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oasis' Okubo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about Miyuki Nakajima?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:43.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Using Miyuki Nakajima's famous song "FIGHT!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:47.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She lectures I AM Noda, a junior
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The phrase "FIGHT!" is a good one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:55.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to say "please keep fighting" to him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:58.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it should work
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How will it turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was a few years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You once asked me for advice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:10.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You and I talked once, didn't we? Over a drink. \N -Yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:17.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's when you said you wanted to work harder and wanted to enter the R-1 and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But you've always been so comfortable with the status quo. How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:24.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm already 44.  \N-44
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't put more effort into it, it'll be too late
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can I put this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:35.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Shivering in the cold water trying to swim upstream
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:40.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you work that hard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of person talks like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's good to have fire in your belly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're not too old
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the sun shines on the surface of the water, can you see the fish underwater glittering
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:58.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, very beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:04.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}The glow is the fish's scales that have flaked off after being injured and are floating in the water
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:20.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The more damage you suffer, the stronger the light will be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You haven't even been hurt, have you? \N -No, I haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okubo cleverly integrates the lyrics into the dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:33.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And they resonate with Noda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great! He's moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}The fish are going upstream
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very determined
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:46.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you been watching a lot of National Geographic or something lately?  \N-Yeah I have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you still borrowing money?  \N-No
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:56.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A guy I met in the theater company when I was in my 20s
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:11:01.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a way to get an easy loan, like the ones posted on telephone poles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He fell into that trap
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then people came to his door
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:10.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Said that he and his family would never have a place to stay again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Did the debtor tell him that?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this a lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:27.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to discourage you because it happens
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't cause anymore trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He didn't understand it though
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:32.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great, not found out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:36.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}I actually witnessed you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Witnessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You saw? \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Yesterday, on the steps of the tram stop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The concept has changed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:12:00.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems like you can't hold your head up when you walk
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was so shocked that I ran away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Felt scared and ran away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But in Shinjuku... \N -In Shinjuku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shinjuku?  -You weren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:19.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, I wasn't in Shinjuku yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was just scared for no reason then
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought "how did the Noda I knew become like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It wasn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She continues
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:31.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I came across a male producer or someone of a slightly higher status than us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:35.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was invited to drink with him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:39.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}I just thought I'd be better off if I were a guy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:44.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Then I may not have to try so hard to please men
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}I wish I were a man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,7 points?  \N-Streak
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Adding this is impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So strong
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,All of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The score is super high
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still hasn't realized
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:09.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okubo executes a beautiful combo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:08.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it just because Noda is an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Immediately afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:13.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, you and Takeda have a good relationship. \N -Yes, we're very close
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}After all, he has a junior high school education
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is he just a junior high school graduate? No, he went to college, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:22.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that wrong? I wondered
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?  \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I'm wrong?  \N-He'd be happy if you remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not right, he went to college
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:34.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She forcibly attempts to add "after all, he has a junior high school education" to the list
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point there were still five minutes left
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:40.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously, {\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}you can do it, FIGHT! FIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I will, I can do it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}FIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What you are saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB322F0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}FIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:14:00.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really did not expect you to say this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been really enlightening
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:09.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not only does he fail to notice the lyrics, but he also receives a rewarding lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:15.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okubo's impressive performance nets her 86 points
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:21.44,special_Wed_1_1,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\move(720,1012,720,882,0,100)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3C27DF&}The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The lecturer is an important choice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this Wednesday Downtown?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You look really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:32.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't be so happy, tell us what the theory is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't just think that being on this show is great
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time is the real lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:43.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"How to use fish as a metaphor for a sense of futility"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This outlook is accidentally interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also came to participate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shoji Tomoharu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:15:00.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Captain of the Ship" by Tsuyoshi Nagabuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to see this one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is my choice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This will be quite tough
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:06.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Among the many tracks of Tsuyoshi Nagabuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:10.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I chose "Captain of the Ship" because it conveys an extraordinarily strong will
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He will lecture his junior, Garittochu's Kumagai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:18.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kumagai also knows that I am particularly fond of Tsuyoshi Nagabuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:26.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I sang this song several times when we went to karaoke
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will it be too obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:27.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Might be tough
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So this is a bit worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you decided what you want as a moving gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to be so polite
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just say, just say
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:58.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't act like you're embarrassed to ask \N-OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.  \N-Okay, I get it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:07.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"What do you want as a moving gift?" The answer is too slow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus begins the lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:17.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have concerns about interacting with everyone, and you're limiting yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The lyrics start from here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:22.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I feel like you do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should say what you want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:31.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Even if someone frowns and says you "love to be in the limelight"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}it's much better than saying "you are a good person"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:39.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Even if someone frowns at you{\c&H1A01D4&} and scolds you{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4} for being in the limelight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it's wrong here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:48.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Those long-winded arguments will also follow you later
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:57.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'll make seniors and juniors worry about you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Not up, not down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:05.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Nor to the right or to the left, you just keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:11.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}and not to the right or to the left {\c&H1A01D4&}you just keep going all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:12.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Two versions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:19.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Before you say believe in me, you must love the self that can always believe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:24.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1A01D4&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Before releasing the words that {\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}you believe in me{\c&H1A01D4&} before{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4} you must love the self that can always believe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:29.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,, {\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Happiness is not something to be but something to feel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you underestimating me?  \N-No, really
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:39.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You despise all human beings, not just me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really don't underestimate the human race
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Don't underestimate humans
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What were we before becoming comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Human beings  \N-Human beings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're human, right?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hot blooded
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}In the end, you and I are just human beings
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Don't look at human beings with such rotten eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've been dead for almost 3 years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:12.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's been as long as 3 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Live well  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE32F1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur4}Live on, live on, live wonderfully
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok... Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The passionate lecture continues
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,30 minutes have passed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:34.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't realise
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:35.09,special_Wed_1_1,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\move(720,1012,720,882,0,100)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3C27DF&}The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:38.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How do you feel after listening to Shoji's words just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:43.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is so angry, has he been under a lot of stress recently
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:52.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Talking about life and death, it was a bit much
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:56.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When explaining himself, what he was saying seemed pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:06.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The scores are as follows, Okubo ranks first with FIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think Asahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:15.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, at the end of the day, everyone was overwhelmed by passionate emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fact that they were lyrics didn't really matter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:20.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They just paid attention to the emotions and didn't realise
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, you could get "Yosoro" in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:25.98,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Nautical term meaning "keep going straight" also appears in the lyrics of "Captain of the Ship".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Yosoro" is impossible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can you do it without "Yosoro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's too tough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you added it, the score would be very high
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:33.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That'd be like giving the song's personal details out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kakuta, as a fan of Tsuyoshi Nagabuchi, do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:40.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was amazing, but I don't want to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Watching was enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:47.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In addition, additional versions of this lyric project were made prior to the broadcast of this episode
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are so unbelievable
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the second one will also be broadcast in the near future
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:59.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:10.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Chocolate Planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Spray-less version of Ikko
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don da ke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:21.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So much to do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How long are you guys going to mess around
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stop everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's get straight to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:36.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you ever dozed while standing up on the subway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite often actually
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe once
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:41.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although you're dozing off
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whilst being shaken around
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:47.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You won't let go of your hand, right? \N -Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:51.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When you doze off, you'll move but your hands are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anyone collapse.  \N-It's rare
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:57.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no such person who dozes off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? What type of person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One more time. \N -Just dozing off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are no such people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:06.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:11.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we bring you this theory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:17.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you have a strong will, you can control your body even after falling asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:25.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'll keep holding onto the ring because of the will to not let go as its dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at the VTR
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:36.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you have a strong will, you can control your body even after falling asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:43.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This will be verified by holding a rope connected to a basin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very simple construction
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:49.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory is valid if the test subjects can sleep for 1 hour continuously while not letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:53.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive to be able to sleep under these conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:58.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, whether they're asleep or not will be judged by a brain specialist
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:02.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Midnight challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:06.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone, thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:10.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A man that must be mentioned when speaking of tenacity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:13.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yasuda Dai Circus' Chief Yasuda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:14.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks like it might work
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:15.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have a battle plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wearing pajamas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:20.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just keep my brain asleep and right hand awake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:23.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that it will not fall
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:25.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only retain consciousness here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:26.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:29.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only here is awake, the brain is asleep, it can work
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:29.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Simple to say at least
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:30.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:34.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The challenge soon begins
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:37.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fall asleep by sheer willpower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:39.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Letting only the brain sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to fall asleep by willpower?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After maintaining this posture with his eyes closed for 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:48.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A strong alpha wave has appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:51.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The moment this wave breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:54.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He will have fallen asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:59.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Chief is just one step away from sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:01.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:03.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.87,0:23:06.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:09.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The clock starts from here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:17.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Chief, as declared beforehand, continues to hold the rope firmly after falling asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After 5 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.40,0:23:38.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The hand holding the rope relaxes for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before gripping again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:42.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:53.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The same phenomenon continues with a certain frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:56.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now he is in a very unusual state
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:24:02.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's drifting between the sleep state and awake state, these two types of brain waves are appearing simultaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:04.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:07.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, i've been doing these tests for 35 years
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:11.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It rarely happens
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:14.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Chief is indeed a unique individual
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:20.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Chief actually achieves the seemingly impossible state of "half asleep and half awake"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:25.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the position of the basin gradually lowers
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.32,0:24:29.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,17 minutes after falling asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.05,0:24:32.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The basin descends to here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.30,0:24:34.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.86,0:24:45.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's making a "hiss, hiss" noise as it drops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.50,0:24:47.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally "hiss, hiss" and it dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.30,0:24:58.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nice hit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.60,0:25:03.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks like he just woke up.\N  -It's true
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:04.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.92,0:25:07.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFEC3E&\1a&H64&}I messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.32,0:25:09.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Were you holding the rope in your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:13.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think I was confusing reality and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.66,0:25:21.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I had a dream that I couldn't sleep because I was holding onto a rope
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.55,0:25:25.14,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.17,0:25:24.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.14,0:25:27.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.64,0:25:29.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello \N-Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.97,0:25:31.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sunshine Ikesaki
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.55,0:25:38.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ikesaki held the line with his eyes closed for 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.22,0:25:41.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sleeping well
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.00,0:25:42.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sleeping nicely
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:42.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's now asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.85,0:25:53.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As before, he successfully keeps the rope steady
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.57,0:25:57.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks like a sleeping chimpanzee
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.62,0:25:59.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not an animal experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:02.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But if you look closely
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.45,0:26:12.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Little by little, the hand is loosening
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.32,0:26:15.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can see the rope moving slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:21.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, the basin gradually descends
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.70,0:26:27.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After sleeping for 40 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.67,0:26:32.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The basin is almost touching his head
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.15,0:26:35.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.30,0:26:42.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.85,0:26:48.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Turned into a hat
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.58,0:26:49.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let it fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.32,0:26:51.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is...a bit of a strange result, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.59,0:26:55.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not how I thought it'd go
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.87,0:27:01.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately the least harmful interaction between man and basin in the history of variety shows
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.17,0:27:07.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd fallen asleep and woke up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.40,0:27:09.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I better pull it up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.87,0:27:12.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.51,0:27:16.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.42,0:27:15.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.32,0:27:17.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But very real
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.55,0:27:18.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.65,0:27:22.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.37,0:27:29.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The third challenger is Audrey's Kasgua
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.06,0:27:30.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.96,0:27:33.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just need to keep it like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.36,0:27:35.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nothing difficult, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.23,0:27:37.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But confident... it's difficult to say if I am or not
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.73,0:27:39.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was told to do so so I will do it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.94,0:27:41.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's my Wednesday Downtown approach
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.84,0:27:44.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're always saying "wait"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.04,0:27:47.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And telling me stuff like "don't sleep while answering questions"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.14,0:27:49.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'll definitely sleep with this in my hand, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.47,0:27:51.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So good
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.47,0:27:55.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga thinks it's a simple job to do only what is required
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.60,0:28:00.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A look of self confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.37,0:28:05.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But after 1 hour with closed eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.27,0:28:12.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no sign of sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.10,0:28:12.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must be tired after an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.85,0:28:15.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.71,0:28:19.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's just been an hour now. You haven't fallen asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.74,0:28:22.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.78,0:28:25.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't start if you don't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.85,0:28:30.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, yes, the timer starts only after you fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.07,0:28:32.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too aware to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.06,0:28:39.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.33,0:28:44.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been...about 3 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.77,0:28:45.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.70,0:28:47.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.37,0:28:51.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm closing my eyes and saying "must sleep" in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:54.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't this how it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.24,0:28:55.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's making me more sleepy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.95,0:28:59.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm getting there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:00.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The staff want him to sleep quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.90,0:29:04.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, he still can't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.95,0:29:08.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so came the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.57,0:29:09.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.19,0:29:11.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's already 6am \N-Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.53,0:29:14.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You need to get to your next job
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.70,0:29:15.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He talked a big game
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.73,0:29:17.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you're disqualified
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.90,0:29:20.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.60,0:29:25.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I guess it's too tough for me to fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.91,0:29:27.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this way
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.11,0:29:29.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please call me again
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.95,0:29:31.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.08,0:29:33.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are other things that I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.02,0:29:34.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A touch of sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.32,0:29:36.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.27,0:29:40.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.32,0:29:42.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello \N-Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.69,0:29:44.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:48.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Magical Lovely's Noda Crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.63,0:29:51.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you drink
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.10,0:29:53.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'll fall asleep faster
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.00,0:29:55.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sleeping wine \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.87,0:30:01.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Noda also belongs to the group that cannot sleep in new environments
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.21,0:30:04.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So he has some chilled whiskey to get him off to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.28,0:30:09.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.02,0:30:12.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.55,0:30:14.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.69,0:30:17.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.47,0:30:18.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Quick
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:21.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As he's sleeping, the challenge begins
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.32,0:30:23.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.92,0:30:25.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.87,0:30:37.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hurts doesn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.82,0:30:44.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly when falling asleep he pulled the rope down hard
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.67,0:30:49.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the rope broke causing the basin to fall
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.02,0:30:57.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The result was unexpected. In short, the challenge failed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.97,0:31:00.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}I don't even feel the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.40,0:31:02.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it scared me to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.84,0:31:06.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, no
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.21,0:31:08.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.41,0:31:12.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're annoying. I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.68,0:31:15.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}So humiliating...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.82,0:31:18.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't do this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.22,0:31:24.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is Downtown's show... how could I do this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.39,0:31:26.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Noda, are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.36,0:31:28.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're watching
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.23,0:31:32.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now I'd like to have a good sweep.\N  -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.90,0:31:33.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sweep
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.07,0:31:33.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.77,0:31:36.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You seem to be stuttering  \N-Unclear, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.51,0:31:39.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, is this going to be shown?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.48,0:31:42.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You want to show this type of result too? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.67,0:31:49.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He seems to have drunk too much
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.60,0:31:48.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.89,0:31:53.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally I wanted to sleep until... drink until I fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.56,0:31:56.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So humiliating...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.09,0:32:00.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't do this, everyone stop, don't shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.76,0:32:03.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Otherwise no one can go home
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.07,0:32:03.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.63,0:32:07.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one can go home
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.70,0:32:06.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.45,0:32:09.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on? \N -What are you upset about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.40,0:32:12.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I looked sharp when I turned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.91,0:32:18.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So when everyone that came today... no one can go home
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.22,0:32:18.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happened
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.02,0:32:21.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's crying
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.30,0:32:22.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too much pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.22,0:32:25.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this guy? The verification is over. Enough is enough
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.62,0:32:28.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.96,0:32:32.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}I can't drink wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.80,0:32:35.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't drink and still \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.10,0:32:37.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought everyone couldn't go back home
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.77,0:32:40.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Drank to have to fall asleep.  \N-I thought I wouldn't be able to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.40,0:32:44.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you cannot sleep until the morning we cannot go home
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.87,0:32:44.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cute, didn't realize he had such a side
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.81,0:32:46.50,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've got enough footage, it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.58,0:32:49.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But you fell asleep at least  \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.41,0:32:52.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that everyone could get home ok
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.22,0:32:54.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Understood, thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.52,0:32:56.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm so busy... \N -Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.19,0:32:59.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry... everyone is busier
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.62,0:33:03.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just have worries, I... just like to think too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.59,0:33:07.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everyone, please go to bed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.96,0:33:12.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't have the big shots scared because of me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.71,0:33:17.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.37,0:33:21.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone is working
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.10,0:33:22.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not entirely incomprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.08,0:33:26.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Ah... I screwed up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.37,0:33:27.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not going home at all
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.92,0:33:31.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's okay. You didn't mess anything up \N -I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.52,0:33:35.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Noda shows an unexpected side
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.69,0:33:39.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But what exactly is his state of mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.80,0:33:43.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone is in a bit of a bind
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.90,0:33:47.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When a little more sober, we re-listen to what he has to say
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.17,0:33:55.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you know that others suffer because of you, you will cry
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.55,0:34:03.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They are also raised by decent parents so they know not to cause other people trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.25,0:34:06.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Aren't most people good like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.69,0:34:08.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.79,0:34:10.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope everyone can be like that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.89,0:34:12.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry \N-I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.46,0:34:15.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much at this late hour
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.77,0:34:17.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.33,0:34:20.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of project is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.17,0:34:24.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To sum up, although accidents occurred frequently
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.84,0:34:30.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The winner is Sunshine Ikesaki with 41 minutes and 12 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.97,0:34:36.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does everyone think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.02,0:34:38.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Four out of four \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.99,0:34:45.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What sort of mood should I have been in watching the last part?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.13,0:34:50.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've known Noda for a long time but i've never seen him like that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.03,0:34:54.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But he is a sensitive person who takes care of others
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.07,0:34:58.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The staff is in a difficult situation due to not being able to start until the person falls asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.94,0:35:02.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's hard to fall asleep in the first place, isn't it?  \N-Yes, it is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.68,0:35:07.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the staff really had their work cut out for them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.52,0:35:11.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Falling asleep in that situation is very impressive, indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.19,0:35:14.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kakuta is suddenly very serious
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.16,0:35:17.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is not possible to treat Noda Crystal as an ordinary good person
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.53,0:35:19.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you been drinking too?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.46,0:35:21.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No I haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.26,0:35:23.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.97,0:35:30.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for Everyone's Theories
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.94,0:35:32.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next presenter is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.38,0:35:37.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tamura Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.31,0:35:39.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.42,0:35:41.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't this everyone's favorite man?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.18,0:35:42.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've won a prize
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.35,0:35:43.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone's favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.69,0:35:44.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have never met anyone who hates him
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.73,0:35:47.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm like curry
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.86,0:35:48.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.91,0:35:51.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's get to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.35,0:35:55.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I brought a theory related to the station of the monorail
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.13,0:35:56.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it:
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.65,0:36:01.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are no residents whose nearest station is "Meibijo Station" on the Tokyo Monorail
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.65,0:36:01.74,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\a6\pos(720,30)}※Tokyo Monorail：A Tokyo-based railroad company that operates only one route, the Haneda Airport Line
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.28,0:36:06.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.07,0:36:07.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kakuta, do you know of this station?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.84,0:36:09.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I know, because people...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.60,0:36:13.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whenever they go pass they think "I don't think anyone lives here"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.42,0:36:15.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Passing by while thinking? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.59,0:36:19.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think I remember anyone ever getting off there
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.72,0:36:21.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the station exists, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.19,0:36:23.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it exists, Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.29,0:36:25.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is a station located near Haneda Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.92,0:36:31.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The station is surrounded by airport-related facilities and factories
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.38,0:36:34.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The people who work there? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.02,0:36:36.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There should be people who use the station to commute
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.15,0:36:37.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But is it the closest station to anyone's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.54,0:36:40.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If so, there should be people leaving from there in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.30,0:36:42.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.42,0:36:46.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, a survey was conducted around the station
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.51,0:36:50.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about today, Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.01,0:36:52.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I cut my bangs too short
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.17,0:36:54.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the circle is a little small
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.09,0:36:55.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't even speak clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.86,0:36:59.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's summer, so its natural for it to shrink
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.20,0:37:08.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are no residents whose nearest station is "Meibijo Station" on the Tokyo Monorail
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.06,0:37:12.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We immediately went to the station to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.18,0:37:14.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The station is there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.20,0:37:19.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As said, the only buildings or factories near the station are those related to the airport
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.88,0:37:22.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No residential-like structures were found
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.84,0:37:27.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we headed in the direction of the residential area
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.27,0:37:33.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And didn't encounter anyone while walking for 8 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.54,0:37:35.71,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But 8 minutes is an acceptable range
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.98,0:37:37.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally we found passers-by
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.50,0:37:41.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, we are TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.10,0:37:42.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you live near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.91,0:37:44.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.67,0:37:47.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is the nearest station to your residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.14,0:37:50.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tenkubashi
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.41,0:37:52.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You don't use Meibijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.74,0:37:55.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.01,0:37:56.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.85,0:37:58.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tenkubashi
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.96,0:38:00.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tenkubashi
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.66,0:38:02.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tenkubashi
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:05.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The nearest station to the residents here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.34,0:38:06.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The old man just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.69,0:38:08.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As you can see, it's Tenkubashi
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.95,0:38:07.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Was that necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.79,0:38:10.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because he also uses Tenkubashi
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.03,0:38:14.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is true that no one lives closer to Meibijo
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.86,0:38:16.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is the theory true, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.87,0:38:19.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was proven almost straight away
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.19,0:38:23.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, there are other stations in the area
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.92,0:38:29.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Haneda Airport Terminal 1 Station Terminal 2 Station, etc
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.71,0:38:33.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A total of 4 stations are located in the hinterland of the airport
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.70,0:38:37.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, since there are no residences around here either
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.11,0:38:40.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So again, there are no residents whose homes are closest to these stations
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.03,0:38:45.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the survey was extended to the whole of Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.56,0:38:52.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly we found a similar pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.69,0:38:54.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.88,0:39:00.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Umijigaura Station on the JR Tsurumi Line in Yokohama City
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.85,0:39:06.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This station is actually located in the hinterland of the Toshiba factory
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.21,0:39:08.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is a station for Toshiba employees only
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.91,0:39:17.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since there are no residences within 2 km, it is not the closest station to anyone's home
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.94,0:39:21.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Following the model of corporate stations
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.22,0:39:29.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is an unmanned station in Toyoura-cho, Gadatabata-gun, Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.35,0:39:37.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is located at the connection between the mountain and forest tunnels
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:43.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A "small front station" that barely shows its face in a gap of only 80 meters in total length
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.61,0:39:51.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are no roads around the station, and the only way to get to the station is by train
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.31,0:39:55.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you want to walk from the station to the road
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.89,0:39:59.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have to walk for 1 hour in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.83,0:40:09.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In terms of anyone living there, you have to go another 6km down the road to get there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.54,0:40:13.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, no residents would consider this to be the closest station to their homes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.74,0:40:18.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But why exactly is a station located here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.13,0:40:22.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because this place was originally a single line open to traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.67,0:40:27.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the trains weren't staggered, the efficiency of transportation would be affected
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.89,0:40:28.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.77,0:40:31.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The tunnel is very long
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.04,0:40:34.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was used by steam trains previously
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.98,0:40:39.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So there had to be a place for the smoke to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.80,0:40:44.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only a specific amount of smoke could be exhausted while the trains are staggered
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.95,0:40:47.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's why this was set up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.63,0:40:54.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For the above two reasons, the signal station was set up during World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.36,0:40:55.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now it is no longer used
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.69,0:41:04.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the end of the war, it was used as a fishermen's colony for about 100 people in the coastal area at the foot of the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.66,0:41:14.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The station was upgraded to a passenger station, "Koboro Station," with the privatization of the national railroad in 1962
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.81,0:41:16.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.05,0:41:22.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since there are almost no schools and stores, no one has lived here for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.14,0:41:27.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, there exists a small station that no one uses
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.40,0:41:32.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why does it still exist today?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.54,0:41:40.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In fact, in 2015, JR Hokkaido expressed its intention to abolish it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.14,0:41:46.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, in view of the fact that many tourists came to visit the station at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.12,0:41:51.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Toyoura-cho is trying to hold on to the station no matter what, and is actively working on maintenance and management
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.72,0:41:53.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's why it has been kept until now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.29,0:42:01.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The unique railroad structure has captured the hearts of secret area lovers and railroad fans
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.36,0:42:05.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although it's a station that one can't even walk on
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.65,0:42:08.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a potentially popular tourist attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.94,0:42:14.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are many other stations like this that are like secret places
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.89,0:42:21.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A view of the rapid flow of the Kinkawa River is available at the "Lookout Seiryu Station" in Yamaguchi Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.89,0:42:22.86,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.19,0:42:29.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kushiro Wetland Station located in the middle of a large wetland in Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.36,0:42:33.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next: In Shizuoka Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.21,0:42:40.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oodai Lake-san Station" was built in the middle of the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.95,0:42:46.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, this station is definitely not the closest to anyone's home
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.23,0:42:50.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it is relatively popular with tourists
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.21,0:42:56.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Passengers come from all over Japan to enjoy this beautiful scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.05,0:43:03.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although these places are not used by residents, they are perfect as tourist destinations
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.89,0:43:07.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Such stations are located all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.30,0:43:14.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, there is a "Furunan Station" in Hoyan-cho, Ten Shiro-gun, Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.31,0:43:16.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is a station that is not even a tourist attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.13,0:43:20.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Conducted by JR Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.72,0:43:27.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,According to a survey, only a few days in a year has visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.55,0:43:30.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The number of passengers at Furanan Station
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.89,0:43:37.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From the 27th year of Heisei to the first year of Reiwa, it was 0 for 5 consecutive years
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.99,0:43:43.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In other words, this station is not used by any residents or tourists
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.03,0:43:50.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As far as you can see, this station is surrounded by pasture and grassland
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.81,0:43:54.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Almost no one lives near the station now
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.48,0:44:00.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With the development of personal transportation, the number of people using the railroad decreased
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.98,0:44:06.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus it eventually hit 0
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.29,0:44:11.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So what exactly does this station exist for?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.63,0:44:18.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The features of this rare station have attempted to be put to use
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.03,0:44:22.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And ways to attract tourists and keep the station have been sought
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.71,0:44:27.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you done anything to increase the number of tourists
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.64,0:44:33.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We made a mascot with the theme of the secret station
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.60,0:44:40.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is a mascot named " Furfur Meow" at Furunan Station
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.77,0:44:44.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The inspiration for "Furfur Meow"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.66,0:44:45.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.96,0:44:52.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Was the storage cabinet on the platform
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.34,0:44:58.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1300E1&\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\r}\NEven if there is nothing, mascots can still be born
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.10,0:45:01.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, the theory is confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.90,0:45:03.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it holds
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.70,0:45:07.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But because it was established too quickly we had to go a bit further
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.16,0:45:13.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And delve deeper into the existence of such places in Japan
