Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.44,0:45:18.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it's good once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.66,0:45:20.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's bad to finish on saying something is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.82,0:45:24.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The mascot at the end is disgusting
